%% User Authentication and Onboarding
A1(User Authentication & Onboarding) --> A2{Is User Authenticated?}
A2 -- Yes --> A3[Profile Page]
A2 -- No --> A4[Login / Register]
A4 --> A5[Complete Registration]
A5 --> A6[Email Verification]
A6 --> A2

%% E-commerce Flow
B1[E-commerce Flow] --> B2[Browse Products or Plans]
B2 --> B3{Select Product/Plan}
B3 -->|Product| B4[Add Product to Cart]
B4 --> B5[View Cart]
B5 --> B6[Proceed to Checkout]
B6 --> B7[Enter Payment Information]
B7 --> B8[Order Confirmation]
B3 -->|Plan| B9[Subscribe to Plan]
B9 --> B10[Enter Payment Information]
B10 --> B11[Subscription Confirmation]

%% Course Creation Flow
C1[Course Creation Flow] --> C2[Create New Course]
C2 --> C3[Enter Course Details]
C3 --> C4[Add Sections and lessons]
C4 --> C5[Upload Course Content]
C5 --> C6[Set Course Price]
C6 --> C7[Publish Course]

%% Enrollment Flow
D1[Enrollment Flow] --> D2[Select Course]
D2 --> D3[Choose Enrollment Method]
D3 --> D4{Subscription or Purchase?}
D4 -->|Subscription| D5[Verify Active Subscription]
D5 --> D9{Is Subscription Valid?}
D9 -- Yes --> D10[Enroll in Course]
D9 -- No --> D11[Display Error Message]
D4 -->|Purchase| D6[Process Payment for Course]
D6 --> D7[Payment Confirmation]
D7 --> D10[Enroll in Course]
D10 --> D8[Access Course Content]

%% Exam Creation Flow
E1[Exam Creation Flow] --> E2[Create New Exam]
E2 --> E3[Set Exam Title and Description]
E3 --> E4[Choose Exam Type]
E4 --> E5[Add Questions and Answers]
E5 --> E6[Specify Exam Settings]
E6 --> E7[Publish Exam]

%% Assignment Flow
F1[Assignment Flow] --> F2[Create New Assignment]
F2 --> F3[Set Assignment Title and Description]
F3 --> F4[Specify Assignment Details and Due Date]
F4 --> F5[Upload Assignment Resources]
F5 --> F6[Publish Assignment]

%% Test Submission Flow
G1[Test Submission Flow] --> G2[Enroll in Course]
G2 --> G3[View Available Tests]
G3 --> G4[Attempt Test]
G4 --> G5[Answer Questions]
G5 --> G6[Submit Test]
G6 --> G7[Receive Grade]
G7 --> G8[Receive Feedback]
G8 --> G9[Review Test Results]

%% Comments and Reactions Flow
H1[Comments and Reactions Flow] --> H2[View Course Content]
H2 --> H3[Add Comment]
H3 --> H4[Add Reaction to Comment]
H4 --> H5[View Comments and Reactions]
H5 --> H6[Manage Notifications for Comments]

%% Course Interaction Flow
I1[Course Interaction Flow] --> I2[View Course Dashboard]
I2 --> I3[Navigate Course Modules]
I3 --> I4[Complete Lessons]
I4 --> I5[Mark Lessons as Complete]
I5 --> I6[Track Progress]
I6 --> I7[Attempt Exams and Assignments]
I7 --> I8[Receive Completion Certificate]
I8 --> I9[Review and Rate Course]

%% Profile Management Flow
J1[Profile Management Flow] --> J2[View User Profile]
J2 --> J3[Update Profile Information]
J3 --> J4[Change Profile Picture]
J4 --> J5[Update Social Links and Bio]
J5 --> J6[Track Course Progress]
J6 --> J7[View Enrollment History]

%% Notifications Flow
K1[Notifications Flow] --> K2[Receive Notifications]
K2 --> K3[View Notification]
K3 --> K4[Take Action on Notification]
K4 --> K5[Mark Notification as Read]
K5 --> K6[Manage Notification Settings]

%% Transaction Flow
L1[Transaction Flow] --> L2[Initiate Transaction]
